snippet.title: The Eagles of Big Bear (Barron Trump Singing)
snippet.description:
The Eagles of Big Bear 

Check us out on Spotify! https://open.spotify.com/album/3y1CZVxPBVqYl2ljdNVWno?si=lLRWLYbeQcuXD9TQDeKi7A

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Up in Big Bear, high and free,
An eagle’s nest for all to see.
Jackie and Shadow, bold and bright,
Guard their young with endless might.

(Chorus)
Oh, let the eagle fly so high,
A symbol shining in the sky.
We stand as one, both proud and strong,
Together we will carry on.

(Verse 2)
Through wind and rain, through sun and snow,
Their strength and love will always grow.
A nation watches, hearts take flight,
Bound together by this sight.

(Chorus)
Oh, let the eagle fly so high,
A symbol shining in the sky.
We stand as one, both proud and strong,
Together we will carry on.

(Verse 3)
From coast to coast, we stand as one,
Beneath the flag, beneath the sun.
Their soaring wings, our guiding light,
A symbol of our nation's might.

(Chorus)
Oh, let the eagle fly so high,
A symbol shining in the sky.
We stand as one, both proud and strong,
Together we will carry on.

(Verse 4)
So side by side, we watch them rise,
Like hope that never fades or dies.
The eagle’s call, so proud and true,
A song of freedom, red, white, and blue.

(Chorus)
Oh, let the eagle fly so high,
A symbol shining in the sky.
We stand as one, both proud and strong,
Together we will carry on.
[Bridge]
I won’t be silent, I won’t be still,
God belongs here, yes, He will.
From every desk, from every hall,
Let His name be heard by all.

[Chorus]
Let’s bring God back to the schools,
Let His wisdom be the rule.
Through the lessons, through the test,
Only faith can bring our best.
With His light, we will stand,
Guided by His mighty hand.

[Outro]
Raise the banner, lift the sound,
Let His name be all around.
From the classrooms to the halls,
God belongs here, after all.
